Class Anonymize

  • Object
    • AnchorBean<CopyFilesNaming<T>>
      • CopyFilesNaming<AnonymizeSharedState>

  • public class Anonymize
extends CopyFilesNaming<AnonymizeSharedState>
    Copies files to a number 001 002 etc. in the same order they are inputted.

    No shuffling occurs.

    Author:
    feehano
